タイトル: <font size = 5>5th Pyayer Shawl</font>
投稿者　: Nyam@Brell&lt;<a href="mailto:nyam_bountydog@hotmail.com">nyam_bountydog@hotmail.com</a>&gt;
<!-- ドメイン: 165.76.58.25 -->
URL　　 : <a href="http://www.sklc.co.jp/~nya/">http://www.sklc.co.jp/~nya/</a>
登録時間:2001年5月9日10時33分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
昨日のPatchで入った模様なのでLOGとりました。<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what is hurther advance mt reputation with the coldain'<BR>
<BR>
Loremaster Borannin says 'Nyam ! Thank Brell you're here. I was about <BR>
to send one of my Lorekeepers looking for you. It appears that the <BR>
information Tanik acquired is most perilous indeed. The Dain has <BR>
called an emergency session of the council and I must attend. We <BR>
don't have the luxury of waiting for an appropriate task to arise, <BR>
you must advance as soon as possible. Unfortunately, I have neither <BR>
the time, nor the components to fashion the next few shawls for you. <BR>
Ask Rexx Frostweaver about the prayer shawl and follow his direction <BR>
carefully.<BR>
<BR>
Boranninさんは会議に行かなくてはいけないらしく、詳細はRexx Frostweaverに<BR>
聞いてくれとのこと。RexxはBankの部屋にいるベンダーです。<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what is prayer shawl'<BR>
<BR>
Rexx Frostweaver says 'Gather five strands of crystalline silk thread <BR>
and combine them in a sewing kit to make a crystalline silk fiber. <BR>
Take this container and combine a glowing shardworm bile with three <BR>
of the fibers to form a piece of glowing crystalline silk. Five <BR>
pieces of glowing crystalline silk sewn to your fur-lined shawl will <BR>
yield a beautiful silk shawl. Become a master in the art of tailoring <BR>
before risking all you've worked for and be sure to let me inspect <BR>
your work when it's complete. <BR>
<BR>
a glowing shardworm bileという４Slotコンテナをもらえます。<BR>
で問題が・・・。<BR>
crystalline silk x 2 = srystalline silk thread<BR>
silk thread x 5 = silk fiber<BR>
silk fiber x 3 を貰ったコンテナでcombine　= piece of glowing <BR>
crystalline silk<BR>
ここまでくるのにcrystalline silk が30枚・・・。で、<BR>
<BR>
Five pieces of glowing crystalline silk<BR>
<BR>
は5個のpieces of glowing crystalline silkが必要なん??30x5=150????<BR>
pieces of glowing crystalline silkをどうするかも書いてないし。。<BR>
とりあえず蜘蛛ちなそう。
